title: Rio: Rainbow Gate! (Rio - Rainbow Gate!: Reshuffle)
synopsis: The "Howard Resort Hotel" is an entertainment destination where people gather from around the world to grab huge fortunes. In the casino is a beautiful female dealer named Rio Rollins, known far and wide as the "Goddess of Victory".
